results.name: a(n) = common ratio for row n in A112668.
maple: A110738 := proc(n) local a ; if n = 1 then RETURN(1) ; else a := 2 ; while (1-a^n)/(1-a) mod n <> 0 do a := a+1 ; od ; RETURN(a) ; fi ; end: for n from 1 to 80 do printf("%d, ",A110738(n)) : od : # _R. J. Mathar_, Mar 13 2007
